---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import SiteNav from "../components/SiteNav.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Contact | Valerii Tikhomirov"
  lang="en"
  description="Contact details and collaboration notes for backend-focused freelance, contract, and part-time work."
>
  <SiteNav lang="en" showLanguageSwitcher={false} />

  <div class="container">
    <header class="page-intro">
      <p class="eyebrow">Contact</p>
      <h1>The easiest way to reach me is by email.</h1>
      <p class="lead">
        I am most interested in remote, flexible, project-based, contract, or part-time backend-heavy product work.
        A short practical introduction is enough to start the conversation.
      </p>
    </header>

    <section class="section-block">
      <h2>Contact channels</h2>
      <div class="card-grid">
        <article class="site-card">
          <h3>Email</h3>
          <p><a href="mailto:v.tikhomirov.dev@gmail.com">v.tikhomirov.dev@gmail.com</a></p>
          <p>Best for project discussions, scope, and next steps.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="site-card">
          <h3>GitHub</h3>
          <p><a href="https://github.com/tikhomirovv" target="_blank">github.com/tikhomirovv</a></p>
          <p>Useful for public code and side projects.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="site-card">
          <h3>GitLab</h3>
          <p><a href="https://gitlab.com/vtikhomirov" target="_blank">gitlab.com/vtikhomirov</a></p>
          <p>Additional public profile and code history.</p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section-block">
      <h2>What is useful to include</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>A short description of the product or system.</li>
        <li>The backend area or problem that needs attention.</li>
        <li>The expected collaboration format: project-based, contract, or part-time support.</li>
        <li>Anything especially sensitive: billing, live production risk, migrations, or deadlines.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="section-block">
      <h2>What happens next</h2>
      <p>
        If the work looks like a strong fit, I can usually respond with clarifying questions, an initial read on the
        scope, and whether the collaboration format makes sense.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="section-block cta-block">
      <h2>Related pages</h2>
      <p>
        If you are evaluating fit, start with <a href="/selected-work">selected work</a>, <a href="/work-with-me">work with me</a>,
        or the full <a href="/portfolio">resume</a>.
      </p>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>
